title: Ep 29: Expect the Unexpected - What the Marines Can Teach Us
description: Expect the unexpected and whenever possible BE the unexpected. I read that in a Kurt Vonnegut book once, and it has stuck with me for years. What does that mean and how can it help us?
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
